summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Lighting Department, granting an easement to Robert L. Oldright and Thelma L. Oldright, his wife, for access road and utility purposes over and across a portion of the City's transmission line right of way lying within the Stephen Foster Donation Claim No. 38 and the C. C. Lewis Donation Claim No. 37 in Tukwila, Washington.
